CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 7, 1956, page 21, reads: "9. Final night prize winners with various prizes presented by several exhibitors."
TitMainTitle: Group of exhibitors and final night prize winners, including man holding radio, and two women with set of Hallite pots and pans, standing in Syria Mosque for the 1956 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair
